Object: 0x1017 Producer Heartbeat Time
Object Code Variable
Description The producer heartbeat time shall indicate the configured cycle time of the heartbeat produced by the device.

The value shall be given in multiples of 1 ms. The value 0 shall disable the producer heartbeat.

Sub 0x00
Name Producer Heartbeat Time
Data Type UNSIGNED16
Access rw
Defaultvalue 2000
PDO Mapping no

Object: 0x102a NMT inhibit time
Object Code Variable
Description This object shall indicate the configured inhibit time between two subsequent NMT messages. The outstanding NMT services shall be queued and shall be issued in order of their occurrence respecting the configured inhibit time.

The value shall be given in multiples of 100 Î¼s. The value 0 shall disable the inhibit time.

Sub 0x00
Name NMT inhibit time
Data Type UNSIGNED16
Access rw
Defaultvalue 0
PDO Mapping no
